short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Frosmo Preview application for Frosmo users

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Frosmo Preview is a web application that allows you to preview and debug how the Frosmo Platform is working on your site.

For more information about the application, see https://docs.frosmo.com/display/ui/Frosmo+Preview.

For more information about Frosmo, visit https://frosmo.com/.

Note! This extension merely loads the application from a Frosmo server. This extension does not contain the application itself. The application you get from the server is always the latest available production version.
